cs.MS, cs.OM, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.PF 

The paper discusses the analysis of Markovian supermarket models, which are a type of queueing system. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.MS (Mathematical Software). The paper also discusses a system of differential equations and nonlinear equations, which suggests that it may belong to cs.OM (Optimization and Control) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also mentions matrix-analytical methods, which could place it in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.PF (Probability).
